Amnesty's researchers get the dossier; so do three wire services and a U.S. congressman with subcommittee ambitions. The Republic's diplomats spend a difficult month explaining that the disappeared are neither detained nor missing nor a category that exists. Abroad, for the first time, the phrase *guerra sucia* appears in print with Mexico attached.

@ibarra_internacional
title: El frente internacional
subtitle: The Comité Eureka takes the regime's disappeared to the world. A relations weapon aimed straight at the regime's face.
